Every day, thousands of vehicles involved in an accident are towed to the workshops, where an appraiser must assess the damage caused and the cost of repair.
No single accident is the same and calculating the cost of parts and labor hours can be a lengthy and complicated task.
The calculation of repair costs of between 20,000 and 30,000 euros by hand, including parts and working hours, can take up to two or three hours.
On the other hand, with the support of the latest IT tools, it is a matter of minutes.
